Package: manageNimble
Type: Package
Title: Manage Nimble
Version: 0.0
Date: 2025-31-03
Author: Quresh S. Latif, Bryan L. Nuse
Maintainer: Quresh Latif <quresh.latif@birdconservancy.org>
Description: Package containing wrapper functions for Nimble to facilitate Bayesian model fitting. Features include parallel processing, automated or manual checking of convergence and sampling (i.e., Rhat, n_effective), and dumping saved posterior samples to disk to avoid overloading RAM.
Suggests: mcmcOutput, nimble, processx, dplyr, stringr, coda
License: None
